          We offer Natural Diamond, Lab-Grown Diamond, Moissanite, Signity Stones, and Birthstones for all your jewelry needs.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="offer-image">
        <img src="/images/shop-engagement-page/romantic-double-heart-diamond-wrap-rings.jpg" alt="Precious Stones" class="offer-img">
      </div>
